================================ Jongo ===============================

Jongo is a tiny sugar over Mongo Java Driver :
 * Writing 'find' queries as if you were in a Mongo Shell
 * Map Mongo Entities to your POJO (using Jackson or a custom Mapper).

Initializing
------------

```java
Mongo mongo = new Mongo();
DB database = mongo.getDB("jongo");
Jongo jongo = new Jongo(database);
MongoCollection mongoCollection = jongo.getCollection("collection-name");

Iterator<User> users = mongoCollection.find(Query.query("{}"), User.class);
User user = mongoCollection.findOne(Query.query("{}"), User.class);
```

Querying :
----------

```java
//Query with parameters
db.users.find({'last_name': 'Smith'})
mongoCollection.find(query("{'last_name': #}", "Smith"), User.class);

//Query with ObjectId
db.users.find({'_id': ObjectId('47cc67093475061e3d95369d')})
mongoCollection.find(query("{'_id': {$oid: '47cc67093475061e3d95369d'}}"), User.class);

//Sorting
db.users.find({}).sort({last_name: 1})
mongoCollection.find("{'$query':{}, '$orderby':{'last_name':1}}", User.class);

//Limit
db.users.find().limit(10)
mongoCollection.find("{'$query':{}, '$maxScan':2}", User.class);

//Skip

//Conditional Operators
db.users.find({'age' : {$lt: 3}})
mongoCollection.find(query("{'age' : {$lt: 3}}"), User.class);

//Geospacial Operators
db.users.find({'address': {'$near': [0,0], $maxDistance: 5}})
mongoCollection.find("{'address': {'$near': [0,0], $maxDistance: 5}}", User.class);

//Count
db.users.count({'last_name': 'Smith'})
mongoCollection.count("{'last_name': 'Smith'}");

//Distinct
db.users.distinct("address");
mongoCollection.distinct("address", "", Address.class);

//Field Selection
db.users.find({'last_name': 'Smith'}, {'first_name': 1})
mongoCollection.find(new Query.Builder({'last_name': 'Smith'}).fields("{first_name:1}").build(), User.class);
```

